@RnCsmum @HaggleSearch @JikkyKjj https://t.co/oirbWTZ4XV

With this information why would you need a vaccine
@HaggleSearch @JikkyKjj I would like to know the total death rate for last year. They are still not published. I wonder why?

@JikkyKjj @RnCsmum @HaggleSearch Nuvaxovid is a more "traditional" vaccine though, right? Are there specific concerns with that formulation that would not also be a concern with the virus?
(Or, did you or someone you trust already discuss this somewhere?)

@HaggleSearch What's is the population percentage of vax / unvax?
IOW, is 77.4% a bad number?
If 78% of the pop is jabbed, that's a bad number.
If 50%, it's a REALLY bad number.
If 95% jabbed, that's not as bad.

@HaggleSearch @JikkyKjj And in February those triple vaccinated accounted for 23% of all deaths that had vaccination status reported. One some days there were 8-10 deaths of those 💉💉💉alone. https://t.co/yWfRbX7MJt
@JikkyKjj @HaggleSearch Thanks for the helpful reply. Keep up the info!
@HaggleSearch @JikkyKjj Is novavax appearing safer, despite spike basis? Its booster or job decision time, or get 'sick'
